uthors=Adam Wu|publisher=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516135338/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20180312/china-xi-jinping-term-limit-explainer/|archive-date=2022-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

